	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, if someone attempted to replace the 72 pin connector but didnt hook the plastic piece back under the PCB, then that piece wont stay down after re-assembling the unit.
<br />
<br />I accidentally did that to a system I'd given to my sister.
<br />
<br />Al

		

